title.en: Hyouketsukei Koso Saikyou desu! – Chiisakute Kawaii Shishou to Kekkon suru Tame ni Saikyou no Majutsushi wo Mezashimasu

Zero no Majutsushi - S-Rank Yuusha Party o Zenryoku de Support Shiteita no ni Tsuihousareta Saikyou no Majutsushi wa Party Kyoufushou ni Natta no de Zenryoku de Ohitori-sama Musou o Hajimeru Koto ni Shimashita
Dungeon Busters ~Chuunen Otoko desu ga Niwa ni Dungeon ga Shutsugen shita node Sekai wo Sukuimasu~
Potion Kouji ni Sasensareta Ore Renkinjutsushi, Bishoujo ni Rachisare Ikoku de Itsunomanika Eiyuu ni naru
Sekai de Yuiitsu no [Shinken Zukai] na no ni Senryokugai to Yobareta Ore, Kakusei Shita [Shinken] to Saikyou ni Naru
Shinmai Ossan Boukensha, Saikyou Party ni Shinu hodo Kitaerarete Muteki ni Naru.
Uchi no Deshi ga Itsu no Manika Jinrui Saikyou ni Natte-ite, Nan no Sainou Monai Shishou no Ore ga, Sore wo Koeru Uchuu Saikyou ni Go Nintei Sareteiru Kudan ni Tsuite
Potion wa 160 km/h de Nageru Mono! ~Item-gakari no Ore ga Bannou Kaifukuyaku o Touteki suru Koto de Saikyou no Boukensha ni Nariagaru!?~
Dore dake Doryoku Shite mo Mannen Level 0 no Ore wa Tsuihou Sareta ~Shin no Teki to Yobareta Shounen wa, Shachiku Megami to Deatte Saikyou no Chikara wo Te ni Ireru~
Eiyuu-ou, Bu wo Kiwameru tame Tensei su ~Soshite, Sekai Saikyou no Minarai Kishi♀~
Maou Toubatsu Shita Ato, Medachitakunai node Guild Master ni Natta
Nise Seiken Monogatari - Osananajimi no Seijo o Uttara Michizure ni Sareta
Sokushi to Hametsu no Saijaku Majutsushi
Kuni ni Saikyou no Barrier wo Hattara Heiwa ni Narisugite Tsuihousaremashita ~Ore no Mahou ga Yabasugite, Bijo to Mazoku ni Kakomarerun da ga!?~
